# Autonomous execution mode

## Owner role

Owner supervises strategy via `/operations/command` and `/operations/priorities` — NOT execution coordinator.

## Autonomous loop (every cycle)

1. `npm run execution:autonomous-next` — pick next dependency-safe task
2. Implement without asking "what next?"
3. `npm run execution:heartbeat` or `execution:daemon` during long work
4. `npm run execution:heal` on failures
5. `npm run feed:append` at milestones (Russian titles)
6. Continue to next queue item

## ChatGPT escalation

Architecture uncertainty → `npm run review:request` — continue parallel safe work.

## Post-Apply

Immediately `execution:phase --phase coding` and continue queue.

## Priority order

1. strategic-priorities.json + dependencyGraph
2. execution-runtime.json blockers
3. Post-rebuild: route intelligence → stop-zone validation → runtime → overlay → APK

## Russian owner UX

All owner-facing strings human-readable Russian. Code/logs internal English OK.
